					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"What the hell... Was this maternal side of her always just bubbling under the surface?",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"渡酱究竟藏着什么——不为人知的前辈母性让她这样做的吗！？",
